section.div: This application allows you to generate mathematical animations using natural language descriptions. It uses OpenAI's GPT model to convert your descriptions into Manim code, which is then used to create beautiful mathematical animations.
Enveloppe helps you to publish your notes on a GitHub repository from your Obsidian Vault, for free!
